/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cca22d61a772f31fca7d59e9f016932f2f29bf5","tid":306233,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:08:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小池百合子政冶立場係點？如對中國立場？</blockquote><br />\n有排都未夠班選總理，過埋東京2020奧運先講</blockquote><br />\n搬築地都搞咁耐就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n延遲搬築地係加分黎架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係佢自己要攔置搬遷因為新址污染超標，<br />\n呢單野令佢支持度繼續爆升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比著係自民黨安排既人做知事，<br />\n隨時咩都唔理硬過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（前兩任豬瀨直樹舛添要一好似無做過野就落左台咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n石原慎太郎係退自民黨選贏然後做勁耐，<br />\n小池都係選贏退自民黨而家勁受歡迎，<br />\n做幾耐唔知但至少比果兩個無人支持好得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw安倍除左都議會大炒，佢終於畀醜聞燒埋身，繼森友又整單獸醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小池政見應該唔會太親中話晒都自民黨出身，退左當唔會思想都變埋（退左自民既石原直情係中國眼中釘添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</blockquote><br />\n我冇話築地扣分喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反而唔明安倍做咩仲攬住稻田唔炒9佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小池以前都支持拜靖國同修改和平憲法,但退左自民黨立場稍為低調返少少<br />\n同埋好似私下同李登輝好FD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未係時候炒姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />稻田除左立場有d位右過安倍外，佢真係無咩可取之處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />至少絕對唔適合做防衛相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw安倍個位唔係單靠炒左稻田就坐得穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢年突然咁多醜聞，d料都唔係近年既事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但對家民進黨根本無人頂到，小池又剛起，又唔夠人腳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n若果安倍真係醜聞越爆越多越大鑊，<br />\n可能自民黨換大佬變相換首相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後回復一年換一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未必既，呢次對安倍唔係壞事，之前一人獨大太無敵，個個都砌佢，而家有多個真對手，可以轉移視線"},{"pid":"d60b91a0ef8db3a31ac58b4b84fc249ba9757fad","tid":306233,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:10:11.000Z","msg":"日本人真幸福 有靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"910cbc9e4eac0155b6120eb498be95ae6ce8beb1","tid":306233,"uid":119875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:25:15.000Z","msg":"無投票權覺得佢成日係度派傳單 + 嘈到仆街"},{"pid":"fcf7a6d8798df89857f51122067b1fc887feba93","tid":306233,"uid":65275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:54:27.000Z","msg":"幾鍾意安倍 希望佢可以做耐啲"},{"pid":"89cffb8aa126e77a0fb81054170331fe35982097","tid":306233,"uid":77959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:54:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無投票權覺得佢成日係度派傳單 + 嘈到仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宣傳係咁嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f3ccf1d4e07041c30d1da5eec3e92e4fe1fbd5","tid":306233,"uid":62391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:57:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e53ac6b7ba89b9247e611792ca3331dd4b598f02","tid":306233,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:01:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小池百合子政冶立場係點？如對中國立場？</blockquote><br />\n有排都未夠班選總理，過埋東京2020奧運先講</blockquote><br />\n搬築地都搞咁耐就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n延遲搬築地係